# LensTemper Advisory Adapter

LensTemper is available in this repository as a portable skill package, not as a
native Cursor full-review adapter.

Use this rule only when the user asks for LensTemper, a LensTemper-style review,
or an advisory plan/spec review through Cursor.

Required references:

- `docs/hosts/cursor.md`
- `reviews/README.md`
- selected lens prompts under `reviews/lenses/`
- `reviews/reviewer-template.md`

Cursor-only output must be labeled advisory/reference. Do not claim full
LensTemper completion unless a separate Cursor adapter proves fresh reviewer
isolation, per-lens artifacts, validator pass, synthesis pass, and rerun status.
